<mvc:View controllerName="lookfood.resources.main.controllers.ProfessionalManagement" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" 
    xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form"
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">

    <Page title="{i18n>profMgmtPageTitle}" id="pageProfMgmt" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress" noDataText="{i18n>tableProfNoData}">
        <headerContent>
            <Button icon="sap-icon://add" press="onAddProfPress" />
            <Button icon="sap-icon://refresh" press="onRefreshProfPress" />
        </headerContent>
        <content>
            <Table>
                <columns>
                    <Column>
                        <header>
                            <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnName}" />
                        </header>
                    </Column>
                    <Column>
                        <header>
                            <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnSurname}" />
                        </header>
                    </Column>
                    <Column>
                        <header>
                            <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnRole}" />
                        </header>
                    </Column>
                    <Column>
                        <header>
                            <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnCurReview}" />
                        </header>
                    </Column>
                </columns>
            </Table>
        </content>
    </Page>

</mvc:View>